name: JesusCoin
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about?
Jesus Christ forgives your sins, redeems your bad trades, and blesses you with heavenly riches. The world is full of rug pulls and honey pots but Jesus is here to set you free.

What makes your project unique?
Jesus Meme. 3 AI Utilities.

History of your project.
None

What’s next for your project?
We are listed on coinmarketcap, next is to be list on CoinGecko to improve our exposure and branding. Will conduct Get $JESUS Trending on twitter with our memetic power. Media Release at Bloomberg, MarketWatch, Yahoo. Jesus Payment Gateway / Processor

What can your token be used for?
Future use for payment gateway or api access usage for B2B.
